column23: The unidentified proportion is included in 1 case in the amusement park; the initial case of a certain club was later found to be related to tea art, and the unidentified proportion was not included.

Unknown proportions are included in the 3 cases of tea art houses (from different tea art houses). The category of "tea art houses" is actually very vague. I will count the 3 cases that broke out at the beginning as unknown for the time being. The subsequent cases can barely be regarded as clear. Knowledge contact history
At the press conference that day, the man who mentioned a case of "the history of Wanhua activities" was also listed as an unknown source.
No detailed numbers of individual infection sources were released on this day
Starting from this day, the press conference has an additional category of "History of Wanhua Activities", which is not included in the category of "Unidentified Source of Infection"
Including corrected regression numbers, but because the individual infection source numbers of the regression are not listed in detail, they are all listed on the day of release
含校正回歸數，但因沒有詳列回歸之個別感染源數字，故皆列於發布當日
